=pod

=head1 PUBLIC

C<BLM::Series> - generate an arithmetic series as a Bedrock array.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 <plugin:Series>
 <null:months $Series.arithmetic(1,1,12)>

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Returns an array that consists of a series of numbers generated
arithmetically by starting at a given integer, incrementing by a
certain value for a given length.

=head1 METHODS

=head2 arithmetic( start, increment, length )

=over 5

=item * start

Starting value

=item * increment

value to increment by each time

=item * length

number of elements to return

=back

